description.standard: Pop music moves at hyperspeed, and A-List Pop is keeping pace, still breaking the hottest songs every week but with a slick new look. Leading things off is the title track of Taylor Swift’s newly released album Lover. It lulls you in with classic reverb, a slow-dance tempo (waltzers, this is your jam), and lyrics that reveal a sunny optimism, showing she’s a lover and a fighter. As Taylor explains to Apple Music, "I think this song is important right now because it really feels timeless and romantic. It makes me feel like music is about celebrating the moments in our lives when we feel magical connections and loyalty and trust. To sway with your lover in the living room or to daydream on your own...this is one of my favorite songs I’ve ever written.” Add the song to your library now and subscribe to this playlist to stay up on the latest and greatest pop music.
description.short: New look. The hottest pop songs. We can't get enough of Taylor's “Lover.”
